mapproperties.key: Working: - The daughter worked (...) She went out at 8 am and used to come back at 9 in the evening. -
Preparing medication and food for her mother: - The daughter used to leave her the meals done (...) According to her daughter she left her pills in the table -
Out for the day: - I used to come every afternoon but I could not stay the entire day as I have a disabled son. But I used to come to the city centre every day to visit her -
Showering: - She used to dress herself -
At the daycare centre: - As I said, arrangements were made for her to go to the daycare centre, they would pick her up at 9am and at 17h or so in the afternoon thay left her at home -
Resting: - She was a very calm person (...) I used to giver her magazines. She used to put on the TV but it did not entertain her. She used to pass the time half asleep. That was at home -
